  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6412025/" class="title-link">计划生育与教育问题与教育的问题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6412025"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/craner/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u52618754-28.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/craner/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Mr.Craner</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-16"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-16 21:48:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6412025_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   国学社曾经有个很厉害的学长，自幼饱读诗书，对世界史、社会学、宗教、国学都很感兴趣。国学社有次开读书会，题目是“《世说新语》与魏晋风骨”，结果他一个人在讲台上讲了一个多小时，下面的人都安静地听。后来他还主办禅文化沙龙，请了一帮老师去，他做主持，气氛内容都很好...

